_sText:
Here is my first original map, cs_ginkou a bank, not sure how long it took me to make this, but I made it over the course of 1 month.

CTs spawn outside and have to rescue the 4 hostages on the 2nd floor and in the vault(basement), Ts spawn on the 2nd floor and in the basement.  There are rescue zones in each CT spawn.

Credit goes to GIJOE92 & CIUV \|/ 8-Ball
